Name: Archspire
rawData:
Archspire is a Canadian technical death metal band from Vancouver, British Columbia. They are currently signed to Season of Mist. The group has released three studio albums.
The band was formed in 2007 as Defenestrated, but changed their name to Archspire in 2009.
In April 2011, Trendkill Recordings released All Shall Align, the band's first album. It was recorded between May and December 2010 working with producer Stuart McKillop at The Hive studios
